# ── Primary Metadata Source ────────────────────────────────
# You need a TMDB API key for the app to work (free, instant).
# Get yours at: https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
# You can also set this in the app Settings page.
# VITE_TMDB_API_KEY=your_tmdb_api_key_here

# ── Fallback Metadata Source ───────────────────────────────
# OMDb API Key (used when TMDB is unavailable)
# Get yours at: https://www.omdbapi.com/apikey.aspx
# Set this in the app Settings page.

# ── HD Image Source (optional) ─────────────────────────────
# Fanart.tv API Key — adds high-res posters/backgrounds
# Get yours at: https://fanart.tv/get-an-api-key/
# Set this in the app Settings page.

# ── Discovery Lists (optional) ─────────────────────────────
# Trakt.tv Client ID — enhances OMDb fallback discovery
# Create an app at: https://trakt.tv/oauth/applications
# Set this in the app Settings page.
